<body class = "d_background page-gutter">


<h3>Who Won?</h3>
<% if @doll_user_total > @doll_cpu_total %>
<div class="d_winner">
<%= "Your madlib wins!!" %></div>
<% elsif  @doll_cpu_total > @doll_user_total %>
<div class="d_winner">
<%= "The computer's madlib wins!" %></div>
<% else %>
<% @doll_user_total == @doll_cpu_total %>
<div class="d_winner">
<%= "It's a tie!" %></div>
<% end %>

<div class="show-container form-margin">
<div class="show-border">
<h3 class="text-pop-up-top">YOU</h3>

<h5>To scare a friend or foe, unleash this prank using a frightening or average-looking doll:</h5>
<p>Place your <span class="word"><%= Word.find(@doll.word1_id).name %></span> doll of choice in a locker, desk, or other <span class="word"><%= Word.find(@doll.word2_id).name %></span> area of your chosen<span class="word"> <%= Word.find(@doll.word3_id).name %></span> place.</p>
<p>Wait for this person to discover the doll which <span class="word"><%= Word.find(@doll.word4_id).name %></span> while you watch, smile spreading across your <span class="word"><%= Word.find(@doll.word5_id).name %></span> face.</p>


<div class="d_total text-pop-up-right" >
<%= @doll_user_total %>
</div>
</div>

<div class="show-border">
<h3 class="text-pop-up-top">COMPUTER</h3>

<h5>To scare a friend or foe, unleash this prank using a frightening or average-looking doll:</h5>
<p>Place your <span class="word"><%= @cadjectives.sample.name %></span> doll of choice in a locker, desk, or other <span class="word"><%= @cadjectives.sample.name %></span> area of your chosen <span class="word"><%= @cnouns.sample.name %></span> place.</p>
<p>Wait for this person to discover the doll which <span class="word"><%= @cverbs.sample.name %></span>  while you watch, smile spreading across your <span class="word"><%= @cnouns.sample.name %> </span> face.</p>

<div class="d_total text-pop-up-right">
<%= @doll_cpu_total %>

</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="start-again-link">
<a><%= button_to 'START AGAIN', home_path, method: :get, class: 'waves-effect waves-light btn-large btn btn-small' %></a>
<!-- <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn-large">Button</a> -->
</div>
</body>
